  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242875.htm", 
  "description": "<p>在过去四年里，微软不断告诉我们Windows未来将在“三个屏幕和一个云平台”上运行。现在，Windows 8、Windows Phone、Xbox One都在朝着这个目标前进，使用相同的内核， 我们之前曾预测微软会在本周的Build 2013开发者大会上分享更多关于实现此愿景的信息。开发者们需要知道如何跨三个平台创建、互通和发布应用与游戏，而微软则需要开发者们给予新平台强劲的 动力和后劲。在Build大会伊始，我们对Xbox One和Windows PCs可能共享代码抱着特别乐观的态度。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2df38443/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242875.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E9%97%AD%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%8D%E8%B0%88Xbox+One%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%97%A5%E6%B8%90%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E5%BF%83%E7%97%85%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242875.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E9%97%AD%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%8D%E8%B0%88Xbox+One%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%97%A5%E6%B8%90%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E5%BF%83%E7%97%85%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242875.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E9%97%AD%E5%8F%A3%E4%B8%8D%E8%B0%88Xbox+One%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E6%97%A5%E6%B8%90%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BA%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E2%80%9C%E5%BF%83%E7%97%85%E2%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242875.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E9%97%AD%E5%8F