  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242874.htm", 
  "description": "<p>在过去几年中，Android手机依然按照自己节奏有条不紊的发展着。三星、HTC、LG和索尼几家世界知名硬件厂商依然每年都在积极与世界各地的运营商 合作，推出搭载自己基于Android系统二次开发操作界面的顶级旗舰机型。<strong>与此同时，Android系统的“生父”谷歌公司也涉足了硬件市场，不断的推 出搭载原生Android系统的Nexus系列机型，而原生Android系统对于某些钟情于Android的粉丝来说，具有一种特殊的吸引力。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2df38442/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242874.htm&amp;t=%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9FS4%E3%80%81HTC+One%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94+%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82%E6%B2%A1%E5%95%A5%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242874.htm&amp;t=%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9FS4%E3%80%81HTC+One%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94+%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82%E6%B2%A1%E5%95%A5%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242874.htm&amp;t=%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9FS4%E3%80%81HTC+One%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94+%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82%E6%B2%A1%E5%95%A5%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242874.htm&amp;t=%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%89%E6%98%9FS4%E3%80%81HTC+One%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94+%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82%E6%B2%A1%E5%95%A5%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticle