  "description": "<p><strong>据英国每日邮报报道，瑞士科学家每年夏季都在努力保护阿尔卑斯山脉最古老的冰川，目前，科学家对瑞士境内阿尔卑斯山脉罗纳冰川覆盖一层白色毯子，以达到冰川融化最小化的效果。</strong>依据最新裸露岩石勘测数据显示该冰川至少有11500年历史，并且对于气候变化非常敏感。数公里的保护毯覆盖在起伏土堆和远古冰川上，能够抵消逐年温度上升导致的冰川融化效应。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2df38440/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242872.htm&amp;t=%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E9%93%BA%E6%95%B0%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%E9%95%BF%E6%AF%AF%E5%AD%90%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E4%B8%87%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%B0%E5%B7%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242872.htm&amp;t=%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E9%93%BA%E6%95%B0%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%E9%95%BF%E6%AF%AF%E5%AD%90%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E4%B8%87%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%B0%E5%B7%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242872.htm&amp;t=%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E9%93%BA%E6%95%B0%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%E9%95%BF%E6%AF%AF%E5%AD%90%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E4%B8%87%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%B0%E5%B7%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242872.htm&amp;t=%E7%91%9E%E5%A3%AB%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6%E9%93%BA%E6%95%B0%E5%85%AC%E9%87%8C%E9%95%BF%E6%AF%AF%E5%AD%90%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E4%B8%87%E5%B9%B4%E5%86%B0%E5%B7%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.c